The paper focuses on improving the accuracy of a face detection algorithm, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of pre-processing methods to enhance images also involves machine learning techniques (cs.AI) and optimization of algorithms (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper may be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories, as face detection is often used in these fields.
